data.title: "The X Factor" Finalist and Wonderland Actress Carly Rose Sonenclar Offers NYC Solo Concert Aug. 10
data.meta_description: "The X Factor" finalist and young Broadway actress Carly Rose Sonenclar offers a solo concert Aug. 10 at the Best Buy Theater in Times Square as part of The Stand Up for a Cure 2013 Concert Series.
data.text:
The concert benefits the Starlight Children's Foundation NY*NJ*CT, where Sonenclar serves as an ambassador.

Starlight Children's Foundation is a global children's charity dedicated to helping seriously ill children and their families cope with their pain, fear and isolation through entertainment, education and family activities.

Sonenclar, who was the runner-up on the second season of "The X Factor," has been seen on Broadway in Les Mis√©rables and Wonderland.
